{"tid":208331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇台仔成日j日文同韓文同「國語」好似","createTime":"2017-04-19T12:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T13:38:49.000Z","uid":61728,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9733327072c1258b41e4e0370ae2854dfcb7920f","tid":208331,"uid":61728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T12:43:19.000Z","msg":"但係人都知日文同韓文漢字發音係似廣東話多過胡語<br />\n起碼日文同韓文仲keep住入聲音(雖然日文會讀埋出黎)<br />\n同埋唔會咩都j左佢<br />\n<br />\n簡單<br />\n日文: kan tan<br />\n韓文: kan dan<br />\n胡語: jian dan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n江山<br />\n日文: kou zan<br />\n韓文: kan san<br />\n胡語: Jiang shan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n123456789 10<br />\n日文: ichi ni san shi go roku shichi hachi kyuu juu<br />\n韓文: il i sam sa o yuk chil pal gu sip<br />\n胡語: yi er san si wu liu qi ba jiu shi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就算係台語其實都似日文，但台灣後生仔鬼識台語咩<br />\n成日j日文韓文同胡語好少<br />\n但一方面仲笑鳩香港人用既唔係中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e604483fcf1245ce4d830fe5c081fac03faa5d39","tid":208331,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T12:51:01.000Z","msg":"12345678910<br />\n<br />\n粵語似日文咩"},{"pid":"b168775d6ad91bdc27a45c781f7ca53dd78c65c9","tid":208331,"uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T12:57:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>12345678910<br />\n<br />\n粵語似日文咩</blockquote><br />\n絕對似 <br />\n韓文 日文 直拼漢字係會有埋尾音<br />\n例如廣東話嘅束音<br />\n<br />\n胡語係冇<br />\n<br />\n1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815efde38b287ca016971c9e1ffef5a37c747305","tid":208331,"uid":10319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T13:20:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但係人都知日文同韓文漢字發音係似廣東話多過胡語<br />\n起碼日文同韓文仲keep住入聲音(雖然日文會讀埋出黎)<br />\n同埋唔會咩都j左佢<br />\n<br />\n簡單<br />\n日文: kan tan<br />\n韓文: kan dan<br />\n胡語: jian dan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n江山<br />\n日文: kou zan<br />\n韓文: kan san<br />\n胡語: Jiang shan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n123456789 10<br />\n日文: ichi ni san <span style=\"color: red;\">shi</span> go roku <span style=\"color: red;\">shichi</span> hachi kyuu juu<br />\n韓文: il i sam sa o yuk chil pal gu sip<br />\n胡語: yi er san si wu liu qi ba jiu shi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就算係台語其實都似日文，但台灣後生仔鬼識台語咩<br />\n成日j日文韓文同胡語好少<br />\n但一方面仲笑鳩香港人用既唔係中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n4同7有兩個讀音你唔講埋出黎？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c351ec69c00348a893ee07b44ab383c705985fc","tid":208331,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T13:38:25.000Z","msg":"日文最好似係上海話<br />\n蝗語呢啲近一二百年先出現嘅點會似"},{"pid":"d6a77595ee5400240bc4f1f9e61c13e8ba992c1c","tid":208331,"uid":36058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T14:01:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>12345678910<br />\n<br />\n粵語似日文咩</blockquote><br />\nyat yi saam sei ng luk chat pat kau sap"},{"pid":"64b25a86e029bc2e4e84dfdd916b6e50d9236298","tid":208331,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T14:03:57.000Z","msg":"稍為去wiki睇下日文同漢語嘅發展史嘅話<br />\n就唔會話乜嘢相似唔相似<br />\n<br />\n因為有啲漢字嘅發音係模仿傳去日本嗰陣嘅漢語發音，同閩南/廣東/上海話相似係必然咁滯，冇乜嘢值得攞去打飛機啫<br />\n<br />\n又唔見攞訓讀個音嚟講"},{"pid":"1db9f10e7c0d3e651f6b79dea7de2077f6926ef0","tid":208331,"uid":36058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T14:04:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>12345678910<br />\n<br />\n粵語似日文咩</blockquote><br />\nyat yi saam sei ng luk chat pat kau sap</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日文(粵語）： ichi ( yat) ni (yi) san (sam) shi (sei) ngo (ng) roku (luk) shichi (chat) hachi (paat) kyuu (kau) juu (sap)"},{"pid":"6371b315e9d5cf23d31ccfd951b83d7d7443b9e4","tid":208331,"uid":36058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T14:05:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>稍為去wiki睇下日文同漢語嘅發展史嘅話<br />\n就唔會話乜嘢相似唔相似<br />\n<br />\n因為有啲漢字嘅發音係模仿傳去日本嗰陣嘅漢語發音，同閩南/廣東/上海話相似係必然咁滯，冇乜嘢值得攞去打飛機啫<br />\n<br />\n又唔見攞訓讀個音嚟講</blockquote><br />\n上面梗係講緊 音読み 啦"},{"pid":"06c35a654b1ec11cb8f4f892257ae59398d11095","tid":208331,"uid":58,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T14:07:01.000Z","msg":"咁人地係跟當時漢字傳入日本果陣既漢語發音 咁梗係似廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2d838603a2c49ecdd9f93938cfa4ffcc1364908","tid":208331,"uid":36058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T14:09:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>稍為去wiki睇下日文同漢語嘅發展史嘅話<br />\n就唔會話乜嘢相似唔相似<br />\n<br />\n因為有啲漢字嘅發音係模仿傳去日本嗰陣嘅漢語發音，同閩南/廣東/上海話相似係必然咁滯，冇乜嘢值得攞去打飛機啫<br />\n<br />\n又唔見攞訓讀個音嚟講</blockquote><br />\n上面梗係講緊 音読み 啦</blockquote><br />\n「三百」日文係 sambyaku ，粵語係 saampaak<br />\n<br />\n最重要係大家都有 k 音，識粵語學日文好着數，好多音讀詞彙都可以類推其讀音，但只識蝗語就類推唔到，例如「三百」蝗語讀 sanbai ，點都推唔到個 k 音出黎。"},{"pid":"ce06ec6833e1ee8e96ffb5f323aa745bd42dbaa3","tid":208331,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T14:11:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>稍為去wiki睇下日文同漢語嘅發展史嘅話<br />\n就唔會話乜嘢相似唔相似<br />\n<br />\n因為有啲漢字嘅發音係模仿傳去日本嗰陣嘅漢語發音，同閩南/廣東/上海話相似係必然咁滯，冇乜嘢值得攞去打飛機啫<br />\n<br />\n又唔見攞訓讀個音嚟講</blockquote><br />\n上面梗係講緊 音読み 啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個當然知道啦，只不過想講呢啲嘢都拎得去打飛機嘅人好膚淺啫"},{"pid":"fdc3975eeb2583a72779e2e03e440e540ea5e756","tid":208331,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T20:24:02.000Z","msg":"佢地同支那大陸人j緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f24bfaaffbd2d01d24ee88df588ea8ef5aabcc10","tid":208331,"uid":16903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T21:17:17.