dBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T04:40:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>12345678910<br />\n<br />\n粵語似日文咩</blockquote><br />\nyat yi saam sei ng luk chat pat kau sap</blockquote><br />\n係cat唔係chat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26a1ae9022a136f99e27aee3e730b5a8a16f915","tid":208331,"uid":90457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T04:41:37.000Z","msg":"日語同泡語冇乜f音"},{"pid":"d4b58ae12b0600d3fed34be6406f6441acdae944","tid":208331,"uid":22043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T05:12:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日文最好似係上海話<br />\n蝗語呢啲近一二百年先出現嘅點會似</blockquote><br />\n我之前去上海，係飛機上聽到一大班上海人講上海話都覺好似日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e37438fcee08edb8924ace03713666b924c63321","tid":208331,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T13:31:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>日文最好似係上海話<br />\n蝗語呢啲近一二百年先出現嘅點會似</blockquote><br />\n我之前去上海，係飛機上聽到一大班上海人講上海話都覺好似日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日文音讀<br />\n吳音 漢音 唐音 宋音<br />\n有啲似"},{"pid":"bcf44d3e42dbb1a866beeb7a29b6a3913cbf318e","tid":208331,"uid":72725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T13:38:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>客家話最似日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n韓文漢字音最多同音字係客家話<br />\n日文漢字音返而同吳語/閩南語似Ｄ"}]}